NK010(tha)011:0: phur pa rgyud lugs las sgrub pa'i dus kyi nyu le skrod pa'i pho nya sgos bskul bzhugs /
NK010(tha)011:2: sgrub chen gyi dus nyams rtags drug tu mngon pa'i
NK010(tha)011:3: gnyen po gdong can drug gi bskul bya ba ni
NK010(tha)011:6: phur pas gzir ba dang bcas /
NK010(tha)011:8: ye shes sku yi sprul pa ste //
NK010(tha)011:9: rdzu 'phrul ston cing bka' nyan pa'i //
NK010(tha)011:10: dpa' brtul stag gi mgo can la //
NK010(tha)011:11: mi mo stag gi mgo can zhon //
NK010(tha)011:12: bang ni rlung gi bskyod du med //
NK010(tha)011:13: skad ni stong khams khyab par sgrogs //
NK010(tha)011:14: lag pa g.yas na phur pa bsnams //
NK010(tha)011:15: gang la bya ba'i snying la ya //
NK010(tha)011:16: lag pa g.yon na lcags kyu bsnams //
NK010(tha)011:17: gang la bya ba'i snying nas drongs //
NK010(tha)011:18: khams gsum dbang du bsdu ba dang //
NK010(tha)011:19: srid gsum zil gyis gnon pa dang //
NK010(tha)011:20: sgrub la bar chad byed pa rnams //
NK010(tha)011:21: thal ba bzhin du rdul du rlog /
NK010(tha)011:23: ye shes thugs kyi sprul pa gcig /
NK010(tha)011:24: stobs kyi rgyal po seng ge la //
NK010(tha)011:25: mi mo seng ge'i mgo can zhon //
NK010(tha)011:26: bang ni rlung gis bskyod du med //
NK010(tha)011:27: skad ni khams gsum khyab par sgrogs //

NK010(tha)011:61: srid gsum zil gyis gnon pa dang //
NK010(tha)011:62: sgrub la bar gcod byed pa'i bgegs //
NK010(tha)011:63: thal ba bzhin du rdul du rlog /
NK010(tha)011:65: ye shes thugs kyi sprul pa gcig /
NK010(tha)011:66: gsod byed chen mo dred mo la //
NK010(tha)011:67: mi mo dred mo'i mgo can zhon //
NK010(tha)011:68: bang ni rlung gis bskyod du med //
NK010(tha)011:69: skad ni stong khams khyab par sgrogs //
NK010(tha)011:70: lag pa g.yas na phur pa bsnams //
NK010(tha)011:71: gang la bya ba'i snying la ya //
NK010(tha)011:72: lag pa g.yon na lcags kyu bsnams //
NK010(tha)011:73: gang la bya ba'i snying nas drongs //

NK010(tha)011:75: srid gsum zil gyis gnon pa dang //
NK010(tha)011:76: sgrub la bar gcod byed pa'i bgegs //
NK010(tha)011:77: thal ba bzhin du rdul du rlog /
NK010(tha)011:79: ye shes thugs kyi sprul pa gcig /
NK010(tha)011:80: grims byed chen mo gzig mo la //
NK010(tha)011:81: mi mo gzig gi mgo can zhon //
NK010(tha)011:82: bang ni rlung gis bskyod du med //
NK010(tha)011:83: skad ni stong khams khyab par sgrogs //
NK010(tha)011:84: lag pa g.yas na phur pa bsnams //
NK010(tha)011:85: gang la bya ba'i snying la ya //
NK010(tha)011:86: lag pa g.yon na lcags kyu bsnams //
NK010(tha)011:87: gang la bya ba'i snying nas drongs //
NK010(tha)011:88: khams gsum dbang du bsdu ba dang //
NK010(tha)011:89: srid gsum zin gyis gnon pa dang //
NK010(tha)011:90: sgrub la bar gcod byed pa'i bgegs //
NK010(tha)011:91: thal ba bzhin du rdul du rlog /
NK010(tha)011:92: nyams drug rtags drug mi gsal ba'i //
NK010(tha)011:93: ting 'dzin drod nyul chen mo rnams //
NK010(tha)011:94: thams cad ma lus dbang du sdud //
NK010(tha)011:95: nyi ma'i zer la gnod byed pa //
NK010(tha)011:96: 'byung po the'u rang gnod byed lnga //
NK010(tha)011:97: dri dang ngad du bcas pa ldang //
NK010(tha)011:98: tshe la bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK010(tha)011:99: zlog byed stag mo'i ting 'dzin gyis //
NK010(tha)011:100: thal ba bzhin du rdul du rlog /
NK010(tha)011:101: nyi ma gung la gnod byed pa //
NK010(tha)011:102: sa bdag chen mo lag chen yang //
NK010(tha)011:103: lci zhing nyam chung drod dang bral //
NK010(tha)011:104: gung la bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK010(tha)011:105: zlog byed stobs ldan ting 'dzin gyis //
NK010(tha)011:106: thal ba bzhin du rdul du rlog /
NK010(tha)011:107: dgong gi dus na gnod byed pa //
NK010(tha)011:108: btsan gyi pho nya rkang phrin yin //
NK010(tha)011:109: phyad phyod ting 'dzin mi gsal ba //
NK010(tha)011:110: dgong la bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK010(tha)011:111: dran byed chen mo ting 'dzin gyis //
NK010(tha)011:112: thal ba bzhin du rdul du rlog /
NK010(tha)011:113: srod kyi dus na gnod byed pa //
NK010(tha)011:114: bdud kyi rgyal po ma rungs pa //
NK010(tha)011:115: grib so gnag cing rmug par byed //
NK010(tha)011:116: zlog byed g.yag gi ting 'dzin gyis //
NK010(tha)011:117: thal ba bzhin du rdul du rlog /
NK010(tha)011:118: nam phyed bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK010(tha)011:119: ma bdud rgyal po kun tu rgyu //
NK010(tha)011:120: spyugs pa len cing me ru 'bar //
NK010(tha)011:121: nam phyed bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK010(tha)011:122: thal ba bzhin du rdul du rlog /
NK010(tha)011:124: tho rangs bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK010(tha)011:125: tshangs pa chen po'i sprul pa ste //
NK010(tha)011:126: me 'od kun gyi bdag po yis //
NK010(tha)011:127: zlog byed dred kyi ting 'dzin dang //
NK010(tha)011:128: sgrub pa rdzas kyi dam pa yi //
NK010(tha)011:129: tho rangs bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK010(tha)011:130: thal ba bzhin du rdul du rlog /
NK010(tha)011:132: gdug byed gnod pa'i bar chad rnams //
NK010(tha)011:133: dus ma yin par 'byung bar byed //
NK010(tha)011:134: ting 'dzin mi gsal dran pa nyams //
NK010(tha)011:135: zlog byed gzig gi ting 'dzin gyis //
NK010(tha)011:136: thal ba bzhin du rdul du rlog /
NK010(tha)011:139: rtags kyi dri dang the brang dri //
NK010(tha)011:140: bdud kyi nyams dang dngos grub nyams //
NK010(tha)011:141: spar shing dri dang rdzas kyi dri //
NK010(tha)011:142: bar chad 'od dang ma mo'i rtags //
NK010(tha)011:143: btsan gyi sgra dang rig 'dzin gsung //
NK010(tha)011:144: thams cad dus dang nyams dga' dang //
NK010(tha)011:145: rdo rje kha t+w+aam rnge'u chung dang //
NK010(tha)011:146: nyung dkar phur bu zhing lpags dang //
NK010(tha)011:147: gu gul dud pa btang bas 'byung //
NK010(tha)011:148: rab rib med par rab shes na //
NK010(tha)011:149: de nyid ye shes lha yi rtags //
NK010(tha)011:150: gsal la rtog med nyam mi nga //
NK010(tha)011:151: rab rib mi brtan 'gyur ba can //
NK010(tha)011:152: rtags min dngos grub bar chad byed //
NK010(tha)011:153: de nyid bzlog par rab shes bya //
NK010(tha)011:154: yang na ting 'dzin chen po drug /
NK010(tha)011:155: gtso bo'i ting 'dzin chen po dang //
NK010(tha)011:156: mtshams dang sras mchog drug rnams kyi //
NK010(tha)011:157: sngags dang tshig dang phur pa yis //
NK010(tha)011:158: dus rnams kun tu bzlog par bya //
NK010(tha)011:159: yang na sras mchog drug rnams kyis //
NK010(tha)011:160: rim pa bzhin du yang dag bzlog /
NK010(tha)011:161: thams cad kun tu bzlog par bya //
